    BandOps [label="?gbmv (一般带状)\n?sbmv (对称带状)\n?tbmv (三角带状)\n?tbsv (三角带状求解)", fillcolor="#ffffff", color="#2e7d32", shape=box, style="bold,rounded", fontsize=16, penwidth=2.5];

