    PackedOps [label="?spmv (对称打包)\n?spr, ?spr2 (打包rank更新)\n?tpmv (三角打包)\n?tpsv (三角打包求解)", fillcolor="#ffffff", color="#2e7d32", shape=box, style="bold,rounded", fontsize=16, penwidth=2.5];

